s="reactions"></div></div></div></div></div></div><p class="paragraph">Salespeople have access to lots of data...<br/>in my previous article, I told a few stories, but I&#x27;m sure, there are more.</p><div class="not-paragraph"><div class="slogging flex-1 flex flex-col bg-white overflow-hidden"><div class="px-6 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-scroll"><div class="slack flex items-start mb-4 text-3xl"><div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden"><div><span class="user font-bold mr-4"></span><span class="timestamp text-grey text-base"></span></div>  <div class="reactions"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="not-paragraph"><div class="slogging flex-1 flex flex-col bg-white overflow-hidden"><div class="px-6 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-scroll"><div class="slack flex items-start mb-4 text-3xl"><div class="mr-3"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;max-width:100%"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;max-width:100%"><img style="display:block;max-width:100%;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0" alt="" aria-hidden="true" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%2740%27%20height=%2740%27/%3e"/></span><img alt="" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="intrinsic" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%"/><noscript><img alt="" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.slack-edge.com%2F2020-11-17%2F1505140772149_859bce139124872dcea0_48.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Favatars.slack-edge.com%2F2020-